# 📧 AI Email Spam Detection Website - Development Documentation

# Project Title

**AI Email Spam Detection Website**

---

# Objective

Design and develop a modern, responsive, and interactive web application for an Email Spam Detection Machine Learning project.

The website should allow users to enter an email or SMS message, analyze it using the existing trained Machine Learning model, and display the prediction with an engaging user interface.

**Deployment is NOT required.** The application only needs to run locally.

---

# Website Goals

The website should:

* Have a modern AI-inspired design.
* Be fully responsive.
* Provide a clean and interactive user experience.
* Integrate with the existing Python Machine Learning model.
* Display prediction results with confidence and visual feedback.

